      +-------------------------------+
     /                               /
    /       Slach Party 3 !!!       /
   /                               /
  +-------------------------------+

 The more nice party of all the west !!! yehaaa !!

 Here is a nice intro invitation from mankind.
 It will work on every CGX or AGA machines with
 something like 8Mb. Fully tested against buggs !!!
 It need to be boot from Workbench cause it uses
 standard datatypes. Take care, there is a .PNG and
 a .IFF version. Upload the one you want! you need
 the correct datatype to run the demo.


 The Slach Party 3 is a very AMiga-Oriented party
 and will take place at 'la teste de buch', a town
 near arcachon, 80Km from bordeaux, in france,
 from 19 to 22 july 2001. The building where
 everything happens is named "LA PARC DES EXPOSITIONS"
 (it's written on it.)

 yehaa !!

 Very touristic area. the beach is only at 10Km.
 The car park is kept, 600 people can come with
 their machines. Alcohol is allowed !
 Big surprises like c64 DJ, 80's computers museum,
 a lot of crash compos,etc...
  Entrance Fee is only 100FF for french boys on place,
  free for girls and foreigners. 75FF is possible
  if you send us the money before july.


        WHAT ABOUT OUR LOVELY COMPETITIONS?

        Hmm! you can win some big things at the
        party by presenting one of your prods !

             ---- CONFIGURATIONS ----
        Demo & intro: 1 compo PC and 1 amiga.
        FREE Configuration. Even Amiga with PPC.
                ---- LIMITATIONS ----
        Demo     : 10 Mo Maxi
        Intro    : 64 Ko Maxi
        Muzic    : 3 minutes maximum
        Gfx 2D-3D: NO limits
        Anim 3D  : 10 minutes maximum
        WILDcompo: 10 minutes maximum

